Class CiscoNxBgpVrfAddressFamilyConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx.CiscoNxBgpVrfAddressFamilyConfiguration

    public class CiscoNxBgpVrfAddressFamilyConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single address family at the VRF level.

    Configuration commands entered at the CLI config-router-af or config-router-vrf-af levels.
